imdb.plot outline: ELEAGUE is the premium esports tournament and content brand formed in partnership between Turner and IMG. Creating globally-reaching esports events for games such as Counter Strike: Global Offensive, Street Fighter V, Overwatch and Injustice 2, ELEAGUE is the premier destination for esports content.
